OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry with variable
OL,6,Famounts of cloud. Feeling cooler than
OL,7,FMonday around eastern coasts where
OL,8,Fmore in the way of cloud is expected
OL,9,Fat times. Sunny and very warm for
OL,10,FDumfries and Galloway.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry evening and night.
OL,13,FRather cloudy, especially in the east,
OL,14,Fwhile the west will see more in the
OL,15,Fway of clearer spells.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FDry and bright but rather
OL,18,Fcloudy, with the best chance of
OL,19,Fbrighter spells developing during the
OL,20,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
