OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Fand warm or very warm on Thursday with
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Variable cloud with risk
OL,8,Fof a few showers on Friday and
OL,9,FSaturday.
